    h1 Treeview Vue Component
    ul.docs-index
    p Treeview Vue component represents Framework7's <a href="/docs/treeview.html">Treeview</a> component.

    h2 Treeview Components
    p There are following components included:
    ul
      li <code><b>f7-treeview</b></code> - main treeview container
      li <code><b>f7-treeview-item</b></code> - treeview item

    h2 Treeview Properties
    table.params-table
      thead
        tr
          th Prop
          th Type
          th Default
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          th(colspan="4") &lt;f7-treeview-item&gt; properties
        tr
          td toggle
          td boolean
          td
          td Enables treeview item toggle button. By default enabled if there are children item
        tr
          td itemToggle
          td boolean
          td false
          td Enables whole treeview item as toggle
        tr
          td selectable
          td boolean
          td false
          td Makes item selectable
        tr
          td selected
          td boolean
          td
          td Makes item selected
        tr
          td opened
          td boolean
          td false
          td Defines whether the item opened by default or not
        tr
          td label
          td string
          td
          td Item label text
        tr
          td loadChildren
          td boolean
          td false
          td Enable when you need to load children items on open.
        tr
          td link
          td string<br>boolean
          td
          td Enables link and link URL if specified as string. Same as <code>href</code> attribute

        tr
          th(colspan="4") &lt;f7-treeview-item&gt; icon related properties
        +vueLinkIconProps
        tr
          th(colspan="4") &lt;f7-treeview-item&gt; navigation/router related properties
        +vueLinkRouterProps
        tr
          th(colspan="4") &lt;f7-treeview-item&gt; action related properties
